solution:
Since arc $CD$ is $60^\circ$, $\angle CAD = 60^\circ/2 = 30^\circ$.  Since triangle $AOC$ is isosceles with $AO = CO$, $\angle OCA = \angle OAC = 30^\circ$.

[asy]
