Suppose that vectors $\mathbf{a}$ and $\mathbf{b}$ generate the parallelogram.  Then the vectors corresponding to the diagonals are $\mathbf{a} + \mathbf{b}$ and $\mathbf{b} - \mathbf{a}.$

